## @content
``` scss
@mixin do-something {
  font-size : 12px;
  color     : red;
  @content;
}

p {
  @include do-something {
    color : blue;
  }
}
```

``` css
p {
  font-size : 12px;
  color : red;
  color : blue;
}
```

